HEADWORD: Pudder
<hw>Pud"der</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A pother; a tumult; a confused
noise; turmoil; bustle.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧All in a <xex>pudder</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

